headline: Ford Pro, ServiceTitan Partner to Streamline Fleet Management for Trades with Integrated Software
summary: ServiceTitan Inc. (NASDAQ:TTAN) is one of the best IPO tech stocks to buy now. On September 8, Ford Pro, the commercial division of Ford Motor Company (NYSE:F), announced a multi-year partnership with ServiceTitan. The collaboration will result in an integrated software solution that uses embedded modems in model year 2020 and newer Ford commercial vehicles. […]
